cdata.name: Substratum Network
cdata.desc:
Substratum is developing an open-source foundation for the decentralized web, providing free and unrestricted access to content for a new Web 3.0.

The Substratum Network is a worldwide collection of nodes that uses industry-leading cryptography to deliver secure content anywhere, all without the need for VPNs or Tor. Substratumwants torevolutionize the hosting industry with per-request billing via micro transactions, all handled by blockchain technology and artificial intelligence.
